•	PCB Design & Hardware Development – Strengthened proficiency in PCB layout and design using EasyEDA, optimizing circuit efficiency, signal integrity, and manufacturability while integrating microcontroller-based wireless communication.
•	Embedded Systems & Sensor Integration – Enhanced skills in microcontroller programming, sensor calibration, and real-time data processing, ensuring seamless interaction between environmental sensors, storage systems, and user interfaces.
